    dc:description "FIGURES 266–273. Cleruchoides noackae. Lin & Huber. Female (holotype) 266, metasoma dorsal (gastral apex lateral); 267, head anterior; 268, antenna. Male (paratype, TAS, Devonport, 22.ix.1986, L. Hill, ex. Baclozygum?depressum) 269, fore- and hind wing; 270, genitalia; 271, fore leg. Male (paratype, TAS, Devonport, 15.v.1986, L. Hill, ex. Baclozygum?depressum on Eucalyptus globosus) 272, antenna; 273, meso- and metasoma dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5779364/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

